name: Baby Owen
description:
Made for the Shock and Awwww Jam :)

Tickle Baby Owen Wilson in the right spots with your mouse and get his infamous wow's out of his system.

Watch out, though. He has a spot he does not like to be touched that will set him off.

And don't touch his nose too much. He broke it recently.

Notes:

Enter full screen as some elements don't adjust to the aspect ratio.

Credits:

Music - Caketown by Matthew Pablo
